casebody.head_matter:
Fabian SANTIAGO, Petitioner,
v.
Arthur F. HILL, Associate Judge, Circuit Court of Illinois, Cook County.
No. 19-6844.
Supreme Court of the United States.
February 24, 2020
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Illinois dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
